00:41:04.000 --> 00:41:04.959
test that on CRAN.

00:41:04.959 --> 00:41:10.639
So I think that's why those are, like, we want to make a little bit of friction, so

00:41:10.639 --> 00:41:16.159
that you have to deliberately choose to use this new testing, use these new conventions,

