00:49:32.320 --> 00:49:36.000
Uh, yeah, so that was kind of, so there's no limit on the size.

00:49:37.199 --> 00:49:42.479
And I think, you know, generally, you know, you'll, you'll, you will sort of mingle

00:49:43.600 --> 00:49:47.360
Snapshot testing with regular testing, like where you can, like, if this is a list,

00:49:47.520 --> 00:49:49.760
you might want to test that this is a specific value.

00:49:50.320 --> 00:49:56.479
And there's another component of the list that's just a, you know, a big blob that you

