tests are a little bit fragile and kind of break more often than you're otherwise like,

00:50:28.560 --> 00:50:33.280
and that will kind of push you naturally back towards a finer grained unit testing that

00:50:33.280 --> 00:50:35.040
you're, that you're used to and test that.

