So I don't think you want to put like, you know, megabytes of data using this, but certainly

00:50:46.959 --> 00:50:50.800
like kilobytes of data, which would be a pain to put in a test file.

00:50:50.800 --> 00:50:54.080
It's a really nice sweet spot for Snapshot testing.

